import React from 'react';
import PropTypes from 'prop-types';
import clsx from 'clsx';
import { withStyles } from '@material-ui/styles';
import {
    Card,
    CardHeader,
    CardContent,
    CardActions,
    Typography,
    Grid,
    Divider,
    Avatar
} from '@material-ui/core';
import { StatusBullet } from 'components';
import { URI } from './../../../../constants/types';
import styles from './styles';

const statusColors = {
    true: 'success',
    false: 'danger'
};
const PresencesCard = props => {
    const { className, classes } = props;
    return (
        <Card className={clsx(classes.root, className)}>
            <CardHeader
                avatar={
                    <Avatar
                        src={'http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/f8aef9003205946523250a062b54bbb6?s=200&r=pg&d=retro'}
                    />
                }
                title={<Typography variant="h5">He thong thong tin</Typography>}
                subheader={
                        <Typography variant="body2">
                            by She Fen
                        </Typography>
                }
            />
            <CardContent>
                <Grid container justify="space-between">
                    <Grid item xs>
                        <Typography variant="h5" color="textPrimary">
                            12
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary">
                            Chua biet
                        </Typography>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs>
                        <Typography variant="h5" color="textPrimary">
                            12
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary">
                            Total Member
                        </Typography>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs> 
                        <Typography variant="h5" color="textPrimary">
                            12 Noverber 2019
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary">
                            Time Started
                        </Typography>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs>
                        <Typography variant="h5" color="textPrimary">
                            12 Noverber 2019
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary">
                            Time End
                        </Typography>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs>
                        <Typography variant="h5" color="textPrimary">
                            Active
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary">
                            Class status
                        </Typography>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs>
                        <Typography variant="button" color="textPrimary">
                            View
                        </Typography>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </CardContent>
        </Card>
    );
};
export default withStyles(styles)(PresencesCard);
